title: Bug 7752: Export multiple files with the same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
OB: When attempting to export multiple files with the same name but located in different directories to a zip file, the export process fails.
EB: When exporting multiple files with the same name but located in different directories to a zip file, the export process should successfully create the zip file with all the files included.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Have multiple files with the same name but located in different directories.
2. Attempt to export these files to a zip file.
